Description:
You arrive at a cave with impressive carvings on its entrance, depicting several Loa. It appears that the carvings were once painted, but most of the color has faded over time. 

It's now impossible to determine whether the painted sections depicted the feats of the engraved Loas or those of lesser Loas.

A humid breeze carrying a blend of cinnamon and bitterness emanates from the cave. The cave is the largest you have seen in the area and seems to extend deeper than initially anticipated.
DescriptionAction: Do you dare to enter this cave?
